Pucchāmi tanti pucchāmi taṃ yācāmi taṃ ajjhesāmi taṃ pasādemi taṃ, ‘‘kathayassu me’’ti – pucchāmi taṃ. Ādiccabandhūti. Ādicco vuccati sūriyosuriyo 
