Katamo upadhiviveko? Upadhi vuccati kilesā ca khandhā ca abhisaṅkhārā ca. Upadhiviveko vuccati amataṃ nibbānaṃ. Yo so sabbasaṅkhārasamatho sabbūpadhipaṭinissaggo taṇhakkhayo virāgo nirodho nibbānaṃ – ayaṃ upadhiviveko. Kāyaviveko ca vivekaṭṭhakāyānaṃvūpakaṭṭhakāyānaṃ 
