na saṃhareyya, mosavajjaṃ pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya, mosavajjā ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyyāti – mosavajje na niyyetha.

Atha jīvitena paññāya, sīlabbatena nāññamatimaññeti. Athāti padasandhi…pe… padānupubbatāpetaṃ – athāti. Idhekacco lūkhajīvitaṃ jīvanto paraṃ paṇītajīvitaṃ jīvantaṃ atimaññati – ‘‘kiṃ panāyaṃ bahulājīvo sabbaṃ saṃbhakkheti, seyyathidaṃ – mūlabījaṃ khandhabījaṃ phaḷubījaṃ aggabījaṃ bījabījameva pañcamaṃ asanivicakkadantakūṭasamaṇappadhānenā’’ti 
Note { id=70, line='621', referenceLine='268', original='asanīva cakkaṃ dantakūṭaṃ samaṇappadhānenāti (sī.)', type='auto', previous='ti padasandhi…pe… padānupubbatāpetaṃ – athāti. Idhekacco lūkhajīvitaṃ jīvanto paraṃ paṇītajīvitaṃ jīvantaṃ atimaññati – kiṃ panāyaṃ bahulājīvo sabbaṃ saṃbhakkheti, seyyathidaṃ – mūlabījaṃ khandhabījaṃ phaḷubījaṃ aggabījaṃ bījabījameva pañcamaṃ asanivicakkadantakūṭasamaṇappadhānenā’’ti '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='bījabījameva pañcamaṃ asanivicakkadantakūṭasamaṇappadhānenāti'}
	Alternative{lang='sī.', text='asanīva cakkaṃ dantakūṭaṃ samaṇappadhānenāti'}}
. So tāya lūkhajīvitāya paraṃ paṇītajīvitaṃ jīvantaṃ atimaññati.

